  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The time-frame and the follow-up elements after embolization of brain arteriovenous
      malformations are not standardized. Therefore, few reliable follow-up data are available for
      these patients. This study aims at collecting standardized long term data for these
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
